      <description>&lt;p&gt;Until now, I had only a test map with a basic terrain so I decided to dedicate some time to the level design. I started by drafting a map of a small town block in a desert valley. My idea was to create a map with 3 attack paths for the snakes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;One road from the North passing under a railway acting as a barrier&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;One canyon coming from the mountain on the East&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;One road coming from the West&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
